short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Enables screen share when using StarLeaf Click-to-Call on Chrome

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: StarLeaf Click-to-Call allows you to dial any user in the StarLeaf Cloud from your browser. This extension lets you share your screen when using Google Chrome.
